Ghana Pays $368 Million Cedis to Ghana Commercial to Repay Refinery Debt

-- B y   J a s o n   M c L u r e
-- 
2011-03-28T10:26:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-28/ghana-pays-368-million-cedis-to-ghana-commercial-to-repay-refinery-debt.html
Ghana ’s government paid  Ghana
Commercial Bank Ltd. (GCB)  572 million cedis to cover debt owed on
Tema Oil Refinery Ltd., Kojo Thompson, the lender’s chairman,
said at a meeting in Accra today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
